The mention of designing secure communication systems suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) subfield. Finally, the mention of error probabilities suggests that the paper may also be relevant to Multimedia (cs.MM) subfield, which deals with the transmission and processing of multimedia data over networks.
